#: .\snippets.json
msgid ""
"This is an advertisement for OmniCorp \"miniguns\".  It shows a picture of a"
" soldier shoulder firing a N8 Nanogun with an ammo belt, whose legs are "
"hidden inside a massive pile of spent .22 LR casings surrounding him, and is"
" also visibly carrying an UPS linked to the gun.  The caption reads: \"When "
"only a thousand bullets will do it, the N8 Nanogun got you covered. OmniCorp"
" Products.\""
msgstr ""
"这是OmniCorp“迷你枪”的广告。图片展示了一名士兵肩扛发射N8纳米枪，配有弹链，其双腿被周围堆积如山的.22 "
"LR弹壳掩埋，并且明显携带了一个连接到枪上的UPS。标题写道：“当需要一千发子弹时，N8纳米枪为你保驾护航。OmniCorp产品。”"

#: .\snippets.json
msgid ""
"This is an advertisement for OmniCorp submachineguns.  It shows a picture of"
" a commando with a O2038SD, casings leaving it but no muzzle flash or other "
"sign it is being fired.  The caption reads: \"The O2038 submachinegun, tried"
" and approved by many special forces, is also available in 9mm ETC for more "
"stopping power. Now available for police*. OmniCorp Products. *Silenced "
"O2038 models may not yet be available in your state.\""
msgstr ""
"这是OmniCorp冲锋枪的广告。图片展示了一名突击队员手持O2038SD，弹壳飞出但无枪口火焰或其他开火迹象。标题写道：“O2038冲锋枪，经多支特种部队试用并认可，现也提供9mm"
" ETC版本以增强制止力。现可供警方使用*。OmniCorp产品。*消音型O2038型号可能尚未在您所在州上市。”"

#: .\snippets.json
msgid ""
"This is an advertisement for OmniCorp handguns.  It shows a picture of a "
"soldier in power armor with a very large revolver aimed skywards. A burning "
"and crashing attack helicopter is in the background.  The caption reads: "
"\"Anti-Materiel Revolver: truly the most powerful handgun of the world. "
"OmniCorp Products.\" in a much smaller font, it ends with the following "
"note: \"Depicted scenario only plausible with computerized fire control "
"systems integrated to power armor HUD.\""
msgstr ""
"这是OmniCorp手枪的广告。图片展示了一名身穿动力装甲的士兵手持一把非常大的左轮手枪指向天空。背景中有一架燃烧并坠落的攻击直升机。标题写道：“反器材左轮手枪：真正世界上最强大的手枪。OmniCorp产品。”字体更小的部分以以下注释结尾：“描绘的场景仅在与动力装甲HUD集成的计算机化火控系统下才可能实现。”"

#: .\snippets.json
msgid ""
"This is an advertisement for OmniCorp electrothermal-chemical ammunition.  "
"It shows several steel plates with small holes and a smoke trail passing "
"through all of them.  Nearby is a disassembled round with its tiny flechette"
" highlighted.  The caption reads:  \"7.62x51mm EC Orbital. Gotta go fast... "
"faster than the International Space Station. OmniCorp Products.\" in a much "
"smaller font, it ends with the following note: \"Tested in light-gas gun "
"with hydrogen-filled barrel.\""
msgstr ""
"这是OmniCorp电热化学弹药的广告。图片展示了几块带小孔的钢板，一道烟迹穿过所有钢板。旁边是一枚拆解的子弹，其微小飞镖被突出显示。标题写道：“7.62x51mm"
" EC轨道弹。必须快……比国际空间站还快。OmniCorp产品。”字体更小的部分以以下注释结尾：“在充氢枪管的光气枪中测试。”"

#: .\snippets.json
msgid ""
"ANTI-TRUST LAW STOPS MERGER: The so called Omni Consumer Products, which "
"would incorporate Leadworks LLC, OmniCorp and Rivtech, was blocked. While "
"such decision might be reverted by the Supreme Court, for now this corporate"
" behemoth which would become larger than many past monopolies together "
"exists only on paper."
msgstr ""
"反垄断法阻止合并：所谓的Omni Consumer Products（将合并Leadworks "
"LLC、OmniCorp和Rivtech）被阻止。虽然最高法院可能推翻此决定，但目前这个将比许多过去垄断企业总和还庞大的企业巨兽仅存在于纸面上。"

