#: .\items\ammo\223.json
msgid "5.56x45mm  OCG Blackout"
msgid_plural "5.56x45mm  OCG Blackouts"
msgstr[0] "5.56x45毫米 OCG黑弹"

#. ~ Description for {'str': '5.56x45mm  OCG Blackout'}
#: .\items\ammo\223.json
msgid ""
"5.56x45mm ammunition with subsonic 131gr tungsten bullets, a civilian/PDW "
"version of the heavier 5.56 OCG Blackout. Trades range and power for low "
"recoil, noise and good armor penetration."
msgstr ""
"5.56x45毫米弹药，使用亚音速131格令钨芯弹头，是更重的5.56 OCG黑弹的民用/PDW版本。以射程和威力换取低后坐力、低噪音和良好的穿甲能力。"

#: .\items\ammo\223.json
msgid "5.56 OCG Blackout"
msgid_plural "5.56 OCG Blackouts"
msgstr[0] "5.56 OCG黑弹"

#. ~ Description for {'str': '5.56 OCG Blackout'}
#: .\items\ammo\223.json
msgid ""
"5.56x45mm ammunition with subsonic 154gr depleted uranium bullets. While "
"weaker and shorter ranged than dedicated subsonic rounds such as 9x39mm, "
"they are more compact and can cut armor like a hot knife through butter."
msgstr ""
"5.56x45毫米弹药，使用亚音速154格令贫铀弹头。虽然比专用的亚音速弹药（如9x39毫米）威力更弱、射程更短，但它们更紧凑，且能像热刀切黄油一样穿透装甲。"

#: .\items\ammo\22etc.json
