"bullets designed for the Stealth MP. Designed for stopping power and "
"'silence' first, armor penetration second."
msgstr ".22电热化学弹药，使用亚音速100格令钨球弹头，专为隐形MP设计。设计优先考虑停止作用和“静音”，其次为穿甲能力。"

#: .\items\ammo\22etc.json
