"Higher muzzle velocity than .22 LR and great stopping power for such a small"
" round. It becomes relatively 'silent' when fired from specialized guns."
msgstr ".22电热化学弹药，使用33格令空尖弹头。比.22 LR更高的初速，对于如此小的弹头具有出色的停止作用。从专用枪械发射时相对“静音”。"

#: .\items\ammo\22etc.json
msgid ".22 ETC APM"
msgid_plural ".22 ETC APMs"
msgstr[0] ".22 ETC APM"

#. ~ Description for {'str': '.22 ETC APM'}
#: .\items\ammo\22etc.json
msgid ""
".22 Electrothermal-chemical ammunition with 42gr armor-piercing match "
"bullets. Great range and armor penetration for a small handgun round but low"
" stopping power."
msgstr ".22电热化学弹药，使用42格令穿甲比赛弹头。对于小型手枪弹来说具有出色的射程和穿甲能力，但停止作用较低。"

#: .\items\ammo\22etc.json
msgid ".22 ETC micro-flechette"
msgid_plural ".22 ETC micro-flechettes"
msgstr[0] ".22 ETC微型箭弹"

#. ~ Description for {'str': '.22 ETC micro-flechette'}
#: .\items\ammo\22etc.json
msgid ""
"A .22 Electrothermal-chemical cartridge loaded with tiny tungsten flechettes"
" contained within a fragmenting plastic capsule. Short range, very low "
"stopping power but it can hit targets and penetrate armor with greater ease."
msgstr "一种.22电热化学弹药，装填有包裹在易碎塑料胶囊内的微型钨箭弹。射程短，停止作用极低，但能更容易地击中目标并穿透装甲。"

#: .\items\ammo\22etc.json
msgid "handloaded .22 ETC HP"
msgid_plural "handloaded .22 ETC HPs"
msgstr[0] "手工装填.22 ETC HP"

#: .\items\ammo\22etc.json
msgid "handloaded .22 ETC APM"
msgid_plural "handloaded .22 ETC APMs"
msgstr[0] "手装 .22 ETC APM"

#: .\items\ammo\556etc.json
msgid "5.56 DK"
msgid_plural "5.56 DKs"
msgstr[0] "5.56 DK"

#. ~ Description for {'str': '5.56 DK'}
#: .\items\ammo\556etc.json
msgid ""
"5.56x45mm electrothermal-chemical ammunition with 16gr drone killer bullets."
" A hypervelocity round with great range, armor penetration and accuracy, "
"useful for designated marksman and battle rifles."
msgstr ""
"5.56x45毫米电热化学弹药，配备16格令无人机杀手弹头。一种具有极远射程、优异穿甲能力和精准度的超高速弹药，适用于精确射手步枪和战斗步枪。"

#: .\items\ammo\556etc.json
msgid "5.56 Electro Blackout"
msgid_plural "5.56 Electro Blackouts"
msgstr[0] "5.56 电热消音弹"

#. ~ Description for {'str': '5.56 Electro Blackout'}
#: .\items\ammo\556etc.json
msgid ""
"Test item. A preternaturally dense, subsonic 5.56x45mm electrothermal-"
"chemical ammunition with 1466gr AP bullets made from some extradimensional "
"unobtainium."
msgstr "测试物品。一种异常致密的亚音速5.56x45毫米电热化学弹药，配备1466格令穿甲弹头，由某种异次元稀有材料制成。"

#: .\items\ammo\556etc.json
msgid "5.56 SAP"
msgid_plural "5.56 SAPs"
msgstr[0] "5.56 SAP"

#. ~ Description for {'str': '5.56 SAP'}
#: .\items\ammo\556etc.json
msgid ""
"5.56x45mm electrothermal-chemical ammunition with a depleted uranium 154gr "
"subsonic armor piercing bullet. OCG quickly adapted this round to "
"conventional 5.56 NATO and kept producing both before the Cataclysm."
msgstr ""
"5.56x45毫米电热化学弹药，配备154格令贫铀亚音速穿甲弹头。OCG迅速将这款弹药适配至传统5.56 NATO口径，并在大灾变前持续生产这两种版本。"

#: .\items\ammo\556etc.json
msgid "5.56 DK tracer"
msgid_plural "5.56 DK tracers"
msgstr[0] "5.56 DK 曳光弹"

#. ~ Description for {'str': '5.56 DK tracer'}
#. ~ Description for {'str': '7.62x51mm EC HV tracer'}
#: .\items\ammo\556etc.json .\items\ammo\762ec.json
msgid ""
"This ammunition is a one-in-five mix of tracer rounds to help keep the "
"weapon they are fired from on target."
msgstr "此弹药以五比一的比例混入曳光弹，有助于维持发射武器的瞄准轨迹。"

#: .\items\ammo\556etc.json
msgid "reloaded 5.56 DK"
msgid_plural "reloaded 5.56 DKs"
msgstr[0] "复装 5.56 DK"

#: .\items\ammo\556etc.json
msgid "reloaded 5.56 DK tracer"
msgid_plural "reloaded 5.56 DK tracers"
msgstr[0] "复装 5.56 DK 曳光弹"

#: .\items\ammo\762ec.json
msgid "7.62x51mm EC orbital"
msgid_plural "7.62x51mm EC orbitals"
msgstr[0] "7.62x51毫米 EC 轨道弹"

#. ~ Description for {'str': '7.62x51mm EC orbital'}
#: .\items\ammo\762ec.json
msgid ""
"7.62x51mm electrothermal, electrically charged round with a discarding sabot"
" encasing a 4gr microflechette and an integrated liquid core nanoreactor "
"replacing an UPS. Its microflechette accelerates to the point of spontaneous"
" combustion."
msgstr "7.62x51毫米电热充能弹，采用抛弃式弹托包裹4格令微镖箭弹头，并集成液态核心纳米反应堆替代UPS。其微镖箭可加速至自燃状态。"

#: .\items\ammo\762ec.json
msgid "7.62x51mm EC HV"
msgid_plural "7.62x51mm EC HVs"
msgstr[0] "7.62x51毫米 EC 超高速弹"

#. ~ Description for {'str': '7.62x51mm EC HV'}
#: .\items\ammo\762ec.json
msgid ""
"7.62x51mm electrothermal, electrically charged round with a 54gr "
"hypervelocity bullet and a liquid core nanoreactor replacing an UPS."
msgstr "7.62x51毫米电热充能弹，配备54格令超高速弹头及液态核心纳米反应堆替代UPS。"

#: .\items\ammo\762ec.json
