#: .\items\ammo\762ec.json
msgid "reloaded 7.62x51mm EC orbital"
msgid_plural "reloaded 7.62x51mm EC orbitals"
msgstr[0] "复装 7.62x51毫米 EC 轨道弹"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'reloaded 7.62x51mm EC orbital'}
#: .\items\ammo\762ec.json
msgid ""
"7.62x51mm electrothermal, electrically charged round with a discarding sabot"
" encasing a 4gr microflechette and integrated handmade radioactive hazard "
"replacing an UPS. Its microflechette accelerates to the point of spontaneous"
" combustion. Dangerous to shooter and targets alike."
msgstr ""
"7.62x51毫米电热充能弹，采用抛弃式弹托包裹4格令微镖箭弹头，并集成手工放射性危险装置替代UPS。其微镖箭可加速至自燃状态，对射手与目标均构成危险。"

#: .\items\ammo\762ec.json
msgid "reloaded 7.62x51mm EC HV"
msgid_plural "reloaded 7.62x51mm EC HVs"
msgstr[0] "复装 7.62x51毫米 EC 超高速弹"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'reloaded 7.62x51mm EC HV'}
#: .\items\ammo\762ec.json
msgid ""
"7.62x51mm electrothermal, electrically charged round with a 54gr "
"hypervelocity bullet and a handmade radioactive hazard replacing an UPS. "
"Dangerous to shooter and targets alike."
msgstr "7.62x51毫米电热充能弹，配备54格令超高速弹头及手工放射性危险装置替代UPS，对射手与目标均构成危险。"

#: .\items\ammo\762ec.json
msgid "reloaded 7.62x51mm EC HV tracer"
msgid_plural "reloaded 7.62x51mm EC HV tracers"
msgstr[0] "复装 7.62x51毫米 EC 超高速曳光弹"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'reloaded 7.62x51mm EC HV tracer'}
#: .\items\ammo\762ec.json
msgid ""
"7.62x51mm electrothermal, electrically charged round with a 54gr "
"hypervelocity bullet, a handmade radioactive hazard replacing an UPS, plus "
"an one-in-five mix of tracer rounds. Dangerous to shooter and targets alike."
msgstr "7.62x51毫米电热充能弹，配备54格令超高速弹头，以手工放射性危险装置替代UPS，并以五比一比例混入曳光弹，对射手与目标均构成危险。"

#: .\items\ammo\9etc.json
msgid "9x19mm ETC HVHP"
msgid_plural "9x19mm ETC HVHPs"
msgstr[0] "9x19毫米 ETC 高速空尖弹"

#. ~ Description for {'str': '9x19mm ETC HVHP'}
#: .\items\ammo\9etc.json
msgid ""
"9x19mm Electrothermal-chemical ammunition with a 116gr high velocity hollow "
"point bullet. HVHP rounds maximize stopping power at about 150% higher "
"muzzle velocity than conventional 9mm JHP."
msgstr "9x19毫米电热化学弹药，配备116格令高速空尖弹头。HVHP弹种通过约150%高于传统9毫米JHP的初速，最大化停止作用。"

#: .\items\ammo\9etc.json
msgid "9x19mm ETC FMJ"
msgid_plural "9x19mm ETC FMJs"
msgstr[0] "9x19毫米 ETC 全金属被甲弹"

#. ~ Description for {'str': '9x19mm ETC FMJ'}
#: .\items\ammo\9etc.json
msgid ""
"9x19mm Electrothermal-chemical ammunition with a brass jacketed 115gr "
"bullet.  A popular round for military, law enforcement, and civilian use "
"even after almost 150 years, adapted to a new ballistic propulsion "
"technology."
msgstr ""
"9x19毫米电热化学弹药，配备黄铜被甲115格令弹头。这款弹药在近150年间始终是军用、执法及民用领域的流行选择，现已适配新型弹道推进技术。"

#: .\items\ammo\9etc.json
msgid "9x19mm ETC HVAP"
msgid_plural "9x19mm ETC HVAPs"
msgstr[0] "9x19毫米 ETC 高速穿甲弹"

#. ~ Description for {'str': '9x19mm ETC HVAP'}
#: .\items\ammo\9etc.json
msgid ""
"9x19mm Electrothermal-chemical ammunition with a high velocity armor-"
"piercing 60gr bullet, which should suffice for anything besides power armor."
msgstr "9x19毫米电热化学弹药，配备高速穿甲60格令弹头，足以应对除动力装甲外的任何目标。"

#: .\items\ammo\9etc.json
msgid "9x19mm ETC HAPM"
msgid_plural "9x19mm ETC HAPMs"
msgstr[0] "9x19毫米ETC HAPM"

#. ~ Description for {'str': '9x19mm ETC HAPM'}
#: .\items\ammo\9etc.json
msgid ""
"Electrothermal-chemical ammunition with a superalloy 40gr hypervelocity "
"armor-piercing match bullet with a tungsten core. Designed to defeat power "
"armor, it can exceed 1100 meters per second. It is inefficient against "
"unarmored threats."
msgstr "电热化学弹药，采用高温合金40格令超高速穿甲比赛弹头，内含钨芯。专为击穿动力装甲设计，速度可超过每秒1100米。对无装甲目标效率较低。"

#: .\items\ammo\9etc.json
msgid "9x19mm ETC SAP"
msgid_plural "9x19mm ETC SAPs"
msgstr[0] "9x19毫米ETC SAP"

#. ~ Description for {'str': '9x19mm ETC SAP'}
#: .\items\ammo\9etc.json
msgid ""
"Electrothermal-chemical ammunition with a depleted uranium 262gr subsonic "
"armor-piercing bullet. A quiet, heavy, accurate, low recoil round with "
"better armor penetration than HVAP. Negligible overpenetration compensates "
"lower muzzle energy."
msgstr ""
"电热化学弹药，采用贫铀262格令亚音速穿甲弹头。这是一种安静、沉重、精准、低后坐力的弹药，穿甲能力优于高速穿甲弹。可忽略的过度穿透补偿了较低的枪口动能。"

#: .\items\ammo\9etc.json
msgid "reloaded 9x19mm ETC HVHP"
msgid_plural "reloaded 9x19mm ETC HVHPs"
msgstr[0] "重装9x19毫米ETC HVHP"

#: .\items\ammo\9etc.json
msgid "reloaded 9x19mm ETC FMJ"
msgid_plural "reloaded 9x19mm ETC FMJs"
msgstr[0] "重装9x19毫米ETC FMJ"

#: .\items\ammo\9etc.json
msgid "reloaded 9x19mm ETC HVAP"
msgid_plural "reloaded 9x19mm ETC HVAPs"
msgstr[0] "重装9x19毫米ETC HVAP"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'magpin'}
#: .\items\ammo\magpin.json
msgid ""
"3d-printed 4g iron flechette for the GC166 Gauss Carbine by OmniCorp. It is "
"not compatible with nail guns or handcrafted coilguns."
msgstr "OmniCorp为GC166高斯卡宾枪设计的3D打印4克铁制箭形弹。与钉枪或手工线圈炮不兼容。"

#: .\items\ammo\nail.json
msgid "nail"
msgid_plural "nails"
msgstr[0] "钉子"

#: .\items\ammo\nail.json
msgid "flechette"
msgid_plural "flechettes"
msgstr[0] "箭形弹"

#: .\items\ammo\shot.json
msgid "anti-materiel slug"
msgid_plural "anti-materiel slugs"
msgstr[0] "反器材独头弹"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'anti-materiel slug'}
#: .\items\ammo\shot.json
msgid ""
"A custom armor-piercing incendiary slug with an extracted 262gr 9x19mm ETC "
"SAP depleted uranium projectile as its tip, enveloped by a lead outer core "
"which in turn is covered by a copper jacket."
msgstr "定制穿甲燃烧独头弹，弹尖采用提取的262格令9x19毫米ETC SAP贫铀弹头，外层包裹铅芯，再覆以铜被甲。"

#: .\items\ammo\shot.json
msgid "micro-flechette shell"
msgid_plural "micro-flechette shells"
msgstr[0] "微箭弹"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'micro-flechette shell'}
#: .\items\ammo\shot.json
msgid ""
"A shell filled with very tiny tungsten darts, this is a custom hand load for"
" hunting prey made of metal rather than flesh and bones."
msgstr "填充了极细钨制飞镖的弹壳，这是为狩猎金属而非血肉骨骼猎物定制的装药。"

#: .\items\ammo\shot.json
msgid "hardcore slug"
msgid_plural "hardcore slugs"
msgstr[0] "硬核独头弹"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'hardcore slug'}
#: .\items\ammo\shot.json
msgid ""
"A custom armor-piercing slug with an extracted 100gr .22 ETC tungsten ball "
"converted into its tip, enveloped by a lead outer core which in turn is "
"covered by a copper jacket."
msgstr "定制穿甲独头弹，弹尖采用提取的100格令.22 ETC钨球改造而成，外层包裹铅芯，再覆以铜被甲。"

#: .\items\gun\1magmg.json
msgid "OCG GG285 Gauss gun"
msgid_plural "OCG GG285 Gauss guns"
msgstr[0] "OCG GG285高斯枪"

#: .\items\gun\1magmg.json
msgid ""
"A milspec bullpup coilgun which accelerates OmniCorp proprietary 1.06mm "
"magmetal glass flechettes to hypervelocity, fed by an UPS and a 300-round "
"helical magazine. Bulky and heavy due to its capacitor but still compact in "
"length."
msgstr ""
"军用无托线圈炮，可将OmniCorp专有的1.06毫米磁性金属玻璃箭形弹加速至超高速，由UPS和300发螺旋弹匣供弹。因电容器而显笨重，但长度仍较紧凑。"

