msgstr "3 发"

#: .\items\gun\223.json
msgid "OCG QR555-CAR"
msgid_plural "OCG QR555-CAR"
msgstr[0] "OCG QR555-CAR"

#: .\items\gun\223.json
msgid ""
"OmniCorp bullpup QR555 covert ops platform uses new subsonic 5.56 NATO loads"
" in several roles, \"quietly\". The Carbine supports automatic fire, has "
"integrated recoil stock and foregrip, with room for one more underbarrel "
"accessory."
msgstr ""
"OmniCorp无托QR555隐秘行动平台采用新型亚音速5.56 "
"NATO弹药，可“安静地”执行多种任务。卡宾枪型支持全自动射击，配备一体式后坐力枪托和前握把，可额外加装一个下挂配件。"

#: .\items\gun\223.json
msgid "OCG QR555-SMG"
msgid_plural "OCG QR555-SMG"
msgstr[0] "OCG QR555-SMG"

#: .\items\gun\223.json
msgid ""
"OmniCorp bullpup QR555 covert ops platform uses new subsonic 5.56 NATO loads"
" in several roles, \"quietly\". The Submachinegun supports automatic fire "
"and ammo belts, comes with integrated recoil stock, underbarrel laser sight "
"and RM42I bayonet."
msgstr ""
"OmniCorp 无托式 QR555 隐秘行动平台采用新型亚音速 5.56 NATO "
"弹药，可“悄无声息”地执行多种任务。这款冲锋枪支持全自动射击与弹链供弹，配备一体式制退枪托、下挂激光瞄具及 RM42I 刺刀。"

#: .\items\gun\223.json
msgid "OCG QR555-DMR"
msgid_plural "OCG QR555-DMR"
msgstr[0] "OCG QR555-DMR"

#: .\items\gun\223.json
msgid ""
"OmniCorp bullpup QR555 covert ops platform uses new subsonic 5.56 NATO loads"
" in several roles, \"quietly\". The Designated Marksman Rifle features a "
"longer, match-grade barrel and an accurized action, limited to only semi-"
"auto and 2-round bursts."
msgstr ""
"OmniCorp 无托式 QR555 隐秘行动平台采用新型亚音速 5.56 NATO "
"弹药，可“悄无声息”地执行多种任务。这款精确射手步枪配备更长的高精度竞赛级枪管与精调枪机，仅限半自动与两连发点射模式。"

#: .\items\gun\223.json
msgid "OCG QR555-SAW"
msgid_plural "OCG QR555-SAW"
msgstr[0] "OCG QR555-SAW"

#: .\items\gun\223.json
msgid ""
"OmniCorp bullpup QR555 covert ops platform uses new subsonic 5.56 NATO loads"
" in several roles, \"quietly\". The Squad Automatic Weapon has a reinforced "
"barrel, support for ammo belts, a very high rate of fire and comes with "
"integrated forward grip/bipod unit, recoil stock and gyroscopic stabilizer."
msgstr ""
"OmniCorp 无托式 QR555 隐秘行动平台采用新型亚音速 5.56 NATO "
"弹药，可“悄无声息”地执行多种任务。这款班用自动武器采用强化枪管，支持弹链供弹，射速极高，并配备一体式前握把/两脚架单元、制退枪托与陀螺稳定器。"

