msgid_plural "Steyr AUGs"
msgstr[0] "斯泰尔 AUG"

#: .\items\gun\22etc.json
msgid "OCG N8 Nanogun"
msgid_plural "OCG N8 Nanoguns"
msgstr[0] "OCG N8 纳米机枪"

#: .\items\gun\22etc.json
msgid ""
"Six barrels, a 6-round burst mode and a higher cyclic rate of fire than the "
"M134 minigun made this the most iconic firearm of OmniCorp. As long as there"
" are UPS charges for its electrothermal action, it can fire over a thousand "
"bullets from a belt without reload."
msgstr ""
"六根枪管、六连发点射模式以及比 M134 加特林更高的理论射速，使其成为 OmniCorp 最具标志性的枪械。只要其电热化学作用有 UPS "
"供电支持，无需装填即可通过弹链发射上千发子弹。"

#: .\items\gun\22etc.json .\items\gun\9etc.json
msgid "6 rd."
msgstr "6 发"

#: .\items\gun\22etc.json .\items\gun\9etc.json
msgid "low auto"
msgstr "低速全自动"

#: .\items\gun\22etc.json .\items\gun\9etc.json
msgid "high auto"
msgstr "高速全自动"

#: .\items\gun\22etc.json
msgid "OCG N8SD Nanogun"
msgid_plural "OCG N8SD Nanoguns"
msgstr[0] "OCG N8SD 纳米机枪"

#: .\items\gun\22etc.json
msgid ""
"With six integrated suppressors over its six barrels to provide maximum fire"
" support in covert operations, OmniCorp N8SD can bring death by a thousand "
"shots just somewhat louder than paper cuts."
msgstr "六根枪管均配备一体式消音器，为隐秘行动提供最大火力支援，OmniCorp N8SD 能以略高于纸割伤的声响带来千弹齐发的死亡。"

#: .\items\gun\22etc.json
msgid "OCG O2038"
msgid_plural "OCG O2038s"
msgstr[0] "OCG O2038"

#: .\items\gun\22etc.json
msgid ""
"The first electrothermal-chemical submachinegun, OmniCorp O2038 features a "
"very fast 4-round burst mode with a complex mechanism to delay felt recoil "
"and a very large capacity yet compact magazine."
msgstr "首款电热化学冲锋枪，OmniCorp O2038 具备极快的四连发点射模式，通过复杂机械结构延迟后坐力感知，并配备大容量紧凑型弹匣。"

#: .\items\gun\22etc.json
msgid "4 rd."
msgstr "4 发"

#: .\items\gun\22etc.json
msgid "OCG O2038SD"
msgid_plural "OCG O2038SDs"
msgstr[0] "OCG O2038SD"

#: .\items\gun\22etc.json
msgid ""
"The first \"stealth firearm\" developed by OmniCorp, featuring an integrated"
" suppressor without any loss in stopping power or portability. A fine "
"general purpose submachinegun for covert operations."
msgstr "OmniCorp 研发的首款“隐形枪械”，配备一体式消音器，且不损失停止作用或便携性。是隐秘行动中出色的通用冲锋枪。"

#: .\items\gun\22etc.json
msgid "OCG 22XLR"
msgid_plural "OCG 22XLR"
msgstr[0] "OCG 22XLR"

#: .\items\gun\22etc.json
msgid ""
"The first electrothermal-chemical gun to reach the civilian market shortly "
"before the Cataclysm, by OmniCorp. It is more formidable than the size of "
"its .22 rounds would suggest."
msgstr "大灾变前夕由 OmniCorp 推出、首款进入民用市场的电热化学枪械。其威力远超其 .22 口径弹药的尺寸所能暗示的水平。"

#: .\items\gun\22etc.json
msgid "OCG DBR"
msgid_plural "OCG DBR"
msgstr[0] "OCG DBR"

#: .\items\gun\22etc.json
msgid ""
"Over and under Double Barrel Revolver with 12 rounds. Its cylinder has six "
"pairs of over/under chambers aligned with the barrels. Such was OmniCorp's "
"solution to improve the stopping power of .22 ETC in a revolver."
msgstr ""
"上下双管转轮手枪，容弹量 12 发。其转轮设有六对上下排列的弹膛，与双枪管对齐。这是 OmniCorp 为提升 .22 ETC "
"弹药在转轮手枪中停止作用而设计的解决方案。"

#: .\items\gun\22etc.json .\items\gun\9etc.json .\items\gun\shot.json
msgid "double"
msgstr "双发"

#: .\items\gun\22etc.json
msgid "OCG SMP"
msgid_plural "OCG SMP"
msgstr[0] "OCG SMP"

#: .\items\gun\22etc.json
msgid ""
"Designed as a dedicated \"silent\" gun by OmniCorp, The Stealth Machine "
"Pistol is an electrothermal-chemical .22 pistol with an integrated "
"suppressor. A valuable sidearm for covert operatives."
msgstr "由 OmniCorp 设计为专用“静音”枪械，隐形冲锋手枪是一款配备一体式消音器的电热化学 .22 手枪。是隐秘行动人员宝贵的随身武器。"

#: .\items\gun\22etc.json
msgid "OCG Stealth Pistol"
msgid_plural "OCG Stealth Pistol"
msgstr[0] "OCG 隐形手枪"

#: .\items\gun\22etc.json
msgid ""
"OmniCorp Stealth Pistol is surprisingly small even with an integrated "
"suppressor. Made only with composite ceramics and polymers to bypass metal "
"detectors when unloaded at the expense of reliability, a now useless "
"feature."
msgstr ""
"OmniCorp "
"潜行手枪即便整合了消音器也小得出奇。它完全由复合陶瓷与聚合物制成，以便在未装弹时规避金属探测器，但代价是牺牲了可靠性——这一特性如今已毫无用处。"

#: .\items\gun\300.json
msgid "M2010 ESR"
msgid_plural "M2010 ESR"
msgstr[0] "M2010 ESR"

#: .\items\gun\300.json
msgid "OCG SMC300"
msgid_plural "OCG SMC300s"
msgstr[0] "OCG SMC300"

#: .\items\gun\300.json
msgid ""
"Stockless Marksman Carbine, the first gun among OmniCorp products, is a "
"selective-fire \"sidearm\" which shares magazines with sniper rifles. "
"Includes critically needed gyroscopic stabilizer. This .300 WM version won "
"three \"Overkill Awards\" from the Guns n Ammo magazine."
msgstr ""
"无托神射手卡宾枪是 OmniCorp 产品线中的首款枪械，作为一款可选射击模式的“副武器”，它与狙击步枪共享弹匣。配备了至关重要的陀螺稳定器。这款 "
".300 WM 版本曾三度荣获《枪械与弹药》杂志颁发的“过度杀伤奖”。"

#: .\items\gun\308.json
msgid "OCG SMC308"
msgid_plural "OCG SMC308s"
msgstr[0] "OCG SMC308"

#: .\items\gun\308.json
msgid ""
"Stockless Marksman Carbine, the first gun among OmniCorp products, is a "
"selective-fire \"sidearm\" which shares magazines with sniper rifles. "
"Includes critically needed gyroscopic stabilizer."
msgstr ""
"无托神射手卡宾枪是 OmniCorp 产品线中的首款枪械，作为一款可选射击模式的“副武器”，它与狙击步枪共享弹匣。配备了至关重要的陀螺稳定器。"

#: .\items\gun\556etc.json
msgid "OCG ADR"
msgid_plural "OCG ADR"
msgstr[0] "OCG ADR"

#: .\items\gun\556etc.json
msgid ""
"The Anti-Drone Revolver is an OmniCorp \"sidearm\" with a carbine length "
"barrel and overcharged electrothermal action, designed to defeat the "
"heaviest among armored drones. Comes with a classic finish in wood."
msgstr ""
"反无人机左轮手枪是 OmniCorp 的一款“副武器”，拥有卡宾枪长度的枪管和过载电热驱动系统，专为击穿最重型的装甲无人机而设计。采用经典的木质饰面。"

#: .\items\gun\556etc.json
msgid "OCG ER555"
msgid_plural "OCG ER555"
msgstr[0] "OCG ER555"

#: .\items\gun\556etc.json
msgid ""
"OmniCorp bullpup ER555 platform uses hypervelocity 5.56 ETC rounds in "
"several roles. The base model on its own is a highly accurate battle rifle "
"with a \"pulsed\" two-round burst mode. Supports aftermarket modifications, "
"but using its conversion kits instead is advised."
msgstr ""
"OmniCorp 无托式 ER555 平台使用超高速 5.56 ETC "
"弹药，可胜任多种角色。基础型号本身便是一款高精度战斗步枪，具备“脉冲式”两连发模式。支持第三方改装，但建议直接使用其转换套件。"

#: .\items\gun\556etc.json
msgid "OCG ER555-ADS"
msgid_plural "OCG ER555-ADS"
msgstr[0] "OCG ER555-ADS"

#: .\items\gun\556etc.json
msgid ""
"OmniCorp bullpup ER555 platform uses hypervelocity 5.56 ETC rounds in "
"several roles. The Anti-Drone Sniper features an overcharged electrothermal "
"action. Comes with integrated forward grip/bipod unit, gyroscopic stabilizer"
" and cheek pad."
msgstr ""
"OmniCorp 无托式 ER555 平台使用超高速 5.56 ETC "
"弹药，可胜任多种角色。反无人机狙击型配备了过载电热驱动系统。自带整合式前握把/两脚架单元、陀螺稳定器和贴腮垫。"

#: .\items\gun\556etc.json
msgid "OCG ER555-CAR"
msgid_plural "OCG ER555-CAR"
msgstr[0] "OCG ER555-CAR"

#: .\items\gun\556etc.json
msgid ""
"OmniCorp bullpup ER555 platform uses hypervelocity 5.56 ETC rounds in "
"several roles. The Carbine supports automatic fire, has an integrated recoil"
" stock and foregrip, with room for one more underbarrel accessory."
msgstr ""
"OmniCorp 无托式 ER555 平台使用超高速 5.56 ETC "
"弹药，可胜任多种角色。卡宾型支持全自动射击，配备整合式后坐力枪托和前握把，并留有一个额外的下挂附件空间。"

#: .\items\gun\556etc.json
msgid "OCG ER555-CQB"
msgid_plural "OCG ER555-CQB"
msgstr[0] "OCG ER555-CQB"

#: .\items\gun\556etc.json
msgid ""
"OmniCorp bullpup ER555 platform uses hypervelocity 5.56 ETC rounds in "
"several roles. The Close Quarters Battle variant supports automatic fire, "
"comes with integrated recoil stock, underbarrel laser sight and RM42I "
"bayonet."
msgstr ""
"OmniCorp 无托式 ER555 平台使用超高速 5.56 ETC "
"弹药，可胜任多种角色。近战型支持全自动射击，配备整合式后坐力枪托、下挂激光瞄准镜和 RM42I 刺刀。"

#: .\items\gun\556etc.json
msgid "OCG ER555-SAW"
msgid_plural "OCG ER555-SAW"
msgstr[0] "OCG ER555-SAW"

#: .\items\gun\556etc.json
msgid ""
"OmniCorp bullpup ER555 platform uses hypervelocity 5.56 ETC rounds in "
"several roles. The Squad Automatic Weapon supports ammo belts, has a "
"reinforced barrel, a very high rate of fire and comes with integrated "
"forward grip/bipod unit, recoil stock, ported barrel and gyroscopic "
"stabilizer."
msgstr ""
"OmniCorp 无托式 ER555 平台使用超高速 5.56 ETC "
"弹药，可胜任多种角色。班组自动武器型支持弹链供弹，拥有加固枪管和极高的射速，并配备整合式前握把/两脚架单元、后坐力枪托、开孔枪管和陀螺稳定器。"

#: .\items\gun\556etc.json
msgid "OCG ER555-SR"
msgid_plural "OCG ER555-SR"
msgstr[0] "OCG ER555-SR"

#: .\items\gun\556etc.json
msgid ""
"OmniCorp bullpup ER555 platform uses hypervelocity 5.56 ETC rounds in "
"several roles. Not that accurate or long ranged for a Sniper Rifle, but "
"unlike most, has a two-round burst mode. Comes with integrated forward "
"grip/bipod unit, gyroscopic stabilizer and cheek pad."
msgstr ""
"OmniCorp 无托式 ER555 平台使用超高速 5.56 ETC "
"弹药，可胜任多种角色。作为狙击步枪，其精度和射程并不突出，但与大多数同类不同，它具备两连发模式。配备整合式前握把/两脚架单元、陀螺稳定器和贴腮垫。"

#: .\items\gun\556etc.json
msgid "OCG ER555-UDD"
msgid_plural "OCG ER555-UDD"
msgstr[0] "OCG ER555-UDD"

#: .\items\gun\556etc.json
msgid ""
"OmniCorp bullpup ER555 platform uses hypervelocity 5.56 ETC rounds in "
"several roles. The Urban Drone Destroyer is very powerful, fast firing but "
"difficult to control in full auto. Comes with integrated recoil stock, "
"ported barrel and gyroscopic stabilizer."
msgstr ""
"OmniCorp 无托式 ER555 平台使用超高速 5.56 ETC "
"弹药，可胜任多种角色。城市无人机毁灭者威力巨大、射速快，但在全自动模式下难以控制。配备整合式后坐力枪托、开孔枪管和陀螺稳定器。"

#: .\items\gun\762ec.json
msgid "OCG AMR"
msgid_plural "OCG AMR"
msgstr[0] "OCG AMR"

#: .\items\gun\762ec.json
msgid ""
"OmniCorp's Anti-Materiel Revolver might be the most powerful handgun ever "
"made. It can destroy almost anything within four shots, but its recoil is so"
" heavy its manual forbids shooting it without wearing power armor."
msgstr ""
"OmniCorp "
"的反器材左轮手枪或许是有史以来威力最大的手枪。它能在四发内摧毁几乎任何目标，但其后坐力极其猛烈，以至于手册中禁止在不穿戴动力装甲的情况下使用。"

#: .\items\gun\762ec.json
msgid "OCG DWOM"
msgid_plural "OCG DWOM"
msgstr[0] "OCG DWOM"

#: .\items\gun\762ec.json
msgid ""
"A battle rifle for future warfare scenarios involving long range "
"engagements, power armor and tank drones, the highly accurate Drone Warfare "
"Opus Magnum can fire two-round bursts of hypervelocity 7.62x51mm EC rounds."
msgstr ""
"这款高精度的无人机战争杰作是一款面向未来战场的战斗步枪，适用于远距离交战、动力装甲和坦克无人机等场景，能够以两连发模式发射超高速 7.62x51mm "
"EC 弹药。"

#: .\items\gun\762ec.json
msgid "OCG MAR7k"
msgid_plural "OCG MAR7k"
msgstr[0] "OCG MAR7k"

#: .\items\gun\762ec.json
msgid ""
"Considered an overkill among overkills, the bullpup Mega Assault Rifle is "
"the most powerful fully automatic rifle of OmniCorp. Even with fixed "
"foregrip and bipod, it is very compact due to a \"CQB\" barrel, a receiver "
"shortened through a vertically sliding bolt and a magazine well right next "
"to its buttplate."
msgstr ""
"这款无托式巨型突击步枪被视为过度杀伤中的极致，是 OmniCorp "
"威力最大的全自动步枪。即便配备了固定前握把和两脚架，它依然非常紧凑，这得益于其“CQB”枪管、通过垂直滑动枪机缩短的机匣，以及紧贴枪托板的弹匣井。"

#: .\items\gun\762ec.json
msgid "OCG OFG16k"
msgid_plural "OCG OFG16ks"
msgstr[0] "OCG OFG16k"

#: .\items\gun\762ec.json
msgid ""
"The Orbital Force Gun is an anti-materiel light-gas rifle with a detachable,"
" vacuum-sealable barrel which can be connected to a hydrogen canister yet "
"works without one with drastically reduced muzzle energy. Its manual "
"recommends avoiding hydrogen despite that due to reliability issues a future"
" OFG16kA1 model would solve."
msgstr ""
"轨道力枪是一款反器材轻气步枪，配备可拆卸的真空密封枪管，可连接氢气罐使用，但即便不连接也能工作，只是枪口动能会大幅降低。其手册建议避免使用氢气，因为可靠性问题将在未来的"
" OFG16kA1 型号中得到解决。"

#: .\items\gun\762ec.json
msgid "OCG Seven-7B"
msgid_plural "OCG Seven-7B"
msgstr[0] "OCG Seven-7B"

#: .\items\gun\762ec.json
msgid ""
"Electrothermal magazine-fed bolt-action anti-materiel rifle. Its "
"hypervelocity 7.62x51mm EC round is not as damaging as a conventional .50 "
"BMG, but its recoil is much lower and its armor penetration better."
msgstr "电热弹匣供弹栓动反器材步枪。其超高速7.62x51毫米EC弹的杀伤力不如传统的.50 BMG，但后坐力低得多，穿甲性能更佳。"

#: .\items\gun\9etc.json
msgid "OCG Desert Eel"
msgid_plural "OCG Desert Eel"
msgstr[0] "OCG Desert Eel"

#: .\items\gun\9etc.json
msgid ""
"This electrothermal-chemical pistol packs a lot of power for its size and "
"weight. As an UPS cannot fit inside a pocket, OmniCorp Desert Eel is a true "
"pocket pistol only for cyborgs with the UPS bionic."
msgstr ""
"这款电热化学手枪在尺寸和重量上蕴含巨大威力。由于UPS无法放入口袋，OmniCorp Desert "
"Eel是专为配备UPS仿生体的赛博格设计的真正口袋手枪。"

#: .\items\gun\9etc.json
msgid "OCG Hand Autocannon"
msgid_plural "OCG Hand Autocannons"
msgstr[0] "OCG Hand Autocannon"

#: .\items\gun\9etc.json
msgid ""
"Bulky, heavy and intimidating, the Hand Autocannon is the most powerful "
"electrothermal-chemical pistol developed by OmniCorp. It has 2 round burst "
"and automatic fire modes."
msgstr "Hand Autocannon体积庞大、沉重且威慑力十足，是OmniCorp研发的最强电热化学手枪。具备2连发点射和全自动射击模式。"

#: .\items\gun\9etc.json
msgid "OCG N9A1 Chaingun"
msgid_plural "OCG N9A1 Chainguns"
msgstr[0] "OCG N9A1 Chaingun"

#: .\items\gun\9etc.json
msgid ""
"OmniCorp biggest \"minigun\" stands out from the Nanogun with its unique "
"trigger group and very flexible burst limiter. Each setting in its fire "
"selector lever can be further tuned through short or long trigger pulls."
msgstr ""
"OmniCorp最大的“迷你炮”以其独特的扳机组和高度灵活的连发限制器区别于Nanogun。其快慢机上的每个档位均可通过短促或长按扳机进一步微调。"

#: .\items\gun\9etc.json
msgid "OCG O2038H"
msgid_plural "OCG O2038Hs"
msgstr[0] "OCG O2038H"

#: .\items\gun\9etc.json
msgid ""
"9mm ETC variant of OmniCorp O2038 SMG. Features more stopping power, recoil,"
" louder gunfire, reduced rate of fire and less rounds per magazine. Utilizes"
" a helical magazine to maximize ammunition capacity."
msgstr ""
"OmniCorp O2038冲锋枪的9毫米ETC变体。具备更强制止力、更高后坐力、更响枪声、降低射速及减少弹匣容量。采用螺旋弹匣以最大化载弹量。"

#: .\items\gun\9etc.json
msgid "OCG O2038HSD"
msgid_plural "OCG O2038HSDs"
msgstr[0] "OCG O2038HSD"

#: .\items\gun\9etc.json
msgid ""
"A 9mm ETC version of the O2038SD with a heavier suppressor, developed "
"together with depleted uranium 9x19mm subsonic armor-piercing rounds. When "
"firing such rounds, it is quieter than the O2038SD, but much louder "
"otherwise"
msgstr ""
"O2038SD的9毫米ETC版本，配备更重的消音器，与贫铀9x19毫米亚音速穿甲弹共同开发。发射此类弹药时比O2038SD更安静，但使用其他弹药则响亮得多。"

#: .\items\gun\9etc.json
msgid "OCG O9 Electromagnum"
msgid_plural "OCG O9 Electromagnum"
msgstr[0] "OCG O9 Electromagnum"

#: .\items\gun\9etc.json
msgid ""
"An electrothermal-chemical revolver from OmniCorp, capable of firing eight "
"9mm bullets at high velocities. Comparable to a .44 magnum or .460 Rowland "
"revolver in performance, but requires a charged UPS."
msgstr ""
"OmniCorp推出的电热化学左轮手枪，能以高速发射八发9毫米子弹。性能堪比.44马格南或.460 Rowland左轮，但需要充电的UPS供能。"

#: .\items\gun\9etc.json
msgid "OCG O9-2 Doublemag"
msgid_plural "OCG O9-2 Doublemag"
msgstr[0] "OCG O9-2 Doublemag"

#: .\items\gun\9etc.json
msgid ""
"A double-barreled yet compact 9mm electrothermal-chemical revolver from "
"OmniCorp. Unlike the .22 DBR, its layout and action allow single shots but "
"impairs accuracy and makes it less reliable."
msgstr "OmniCorp推出的双管紧凑型9毫米电热化学左轮手枪。与.22 DBR不同，其布局和结构允许单发射击，但会降低精度并影响可靠性。"

#: .\items\gun\9etc.json
msgid "single"
msgstr "单发"

#: .\items\gun\9etc.json
msgid "OCG MS400 Mini Sniper"
msgid_plural "OCG MS400 Mini Sniper"
msgstr[0] "OCG MS400 Mini Sniper"

#: .\items\gun\9etc.json
msgid ""
"Propelling rounds at muzzle velocities expected from rifle cartridges, this "
"highly accurate 9mm electrothermal-chemical rifle from OmniCorp can mostly "
"fulfill the sniper role in urban environments."
msgstr "这款OmniCorp高精度9毫米电热化学步枪能以步枪弹的初速发射子弹，在城市环境中基本能胜任狙击任务。"

#: .\items\gun\9etc.json
msgid "OCG MS400SD Boatman"
msgid_plural "OCG MS400SD Boatman"
msgstr[0] "OCG MS400SD Boatman"

#: .\items\gun\9etc.json
msgid ""
"This variant of the MS400 Mini Sniper is deadly accurate and \"silent\" even"
" with hypersonic rounds. A great OmniCorp product for 6'+ tall bald hitmen "
"or zombie apocalypse survivors."
msgstr ""
"MS400 Mini "
"Sniper的变体，即使使用高超音速弹药也致命精准且“寂静”。是OmniCorp为身高6英尺以上的光头杀手或僵尸末日幸存者打造的绝佳产品。"

#: .\items\gun\9etc.json
msgid "OCG Super SMG"
msgid_plural "OCG Super SMGs"
msgstr[0] "OCG Super SMG"

#: .\items\gun\9etc.json
msgid ""
"\"Puts the machinegun in submachinegun\" - OmniCorp marketing pitch. "
"Compatible with ammo belts, the SSMG is very bulky but can almost match a "
"5.56x45mm machinegun's stopping power. Features integrated combined forward "
"grip/bipod unit and a roomy magazine well."
msgstr ""
"“将机枪塞进冲锋枪”——OmniCorp宣传语。兼容弹链供弹，SSMG非常笨重但制止力几乎媲美5.56x45毫米机枪。配备集成式前握把/两脚架组合单元及宽敞的弹匣井。"

#: .\items\gun\9mm.json
msgid "OCG Baby Eel"
msgid_plural "OCG Baby Eels"
msgstr[0] "OCG Baby Eel"

#: .\items\gun\9mm.json
msgid ""
"Externally almost identical to the electrothermal Desert Eel, this pocket "
"pistol is very lightweight, but felt recoil is higher than in most 9mm "
"pistols."
msgstr "外观几乎与电热Desert Eel相同，这款口袋手枪非常轻便，但感知后坐力高于大多数9毫米手枪。"

#: .\items\gun\9mm.json
msgid "OCG MR9 DMSMG"
msgid_plural "OCG MR9 DMSMG"
msgstr[0] "OCG MR9 DMSMG"

#: .\items\gun\9mm.json
msgid ""
"OmniCorp MR9 is called a Designated Marksman Submachinegun. It has a very "
"long, match-grade barrel and a highly accurate action. Technically a "
"submachinegun, it resembles and is handled like a rifle."
msgstr "OmniCorp MR9被称为“指定射手冲锋枪”。配备超长竞赛级枪管和高精度枪机。技术上属于冲锋枪，但外形和操作方式类似步枪。"

#: .\items\gun\9mm.json
msgid "OCG MR9S Mini Rifle"
msgid_plural "OCG MR9S Mini Rifle"
msgstr[0] "OCG MR9S Mini Rifle"

#: .\items\gun\9mm.json
msgid ""
"A civilian, semi-automatic version of OmniCorp MR9 DMSMG with the same very "
"long barrel. Some call it a carbine despite its barrel length, others call "
"it a rifle. Either way, it is good for what it is but expensive."
msgstr ""
"OmniCorp MR9 DMSMG的民用半自动版本，保留相同超长枪管。有人因其枪管长度称其为卡宾枪，也有人视作步枪。无论如何，它性能出色但价格昂贵。"

#: .\items\gun\9mm.json
msgid "OCG MR9SD Styx"
msgid_plural "OCG MR9SD Styx"
msgstr[0] "OCG MR9SD Styx"

#: .\items\gun\9mm.json
msgid ""
"Without requiring subsonic rounds and with the same length as the MR9 DMSMG,"
" OmniCorp Styx is a pretty \"silent\" firearm. Weaker and shorter ranged "
"than a rifle caliber one like the VSS Vintorez, it still is useful for "
"covert marksmen."
msgstr ""
"无需亚音速弹药且长度与MR9 DMSMG相同，OmniCorp Styx是一款相当“寂静”的枪械。虽比VSS "
"Vintorez等步枪口径武器威力弱、射程短，但对隐秘射手仍很有用。"

#: .\items\gun\abstract.json
msgid "base ETC pistol"
msgid_plural "base ETC pistols"
msgstr[0] "基础ETC手枪"

#: .\items\gun\abstract.json
msgid "EC ammo ETC revolver"
msgid_plural "EC ammo ETC revolvers"
msgstr[0] "EC弹药ETC左轮手枪"

#: .\items\gun\abstract.json
msgid "ETC revolver"
msgid_plural "ETC revolvers"
msgstr[0] "ETC左轮手枪"

#: .\items\gun\abstract.json
msgid "2 charges ETC revolver"
msgid_plural "2 charges ETC revolvers"
msgstr[0] "2发装药ETC左轮手枪"

#: .\items\gun\abstract.json
msgid "EC ammo ETC rifle"
msgid_plural "EC ammo ETC rifles"
msgstr[0] "EC弹药ETC步枪"

#: .\items\gun\abstract.json
msgid "base ETC rifle"
msgid_plural "base ETC rifles"
msgstr[0] "基础ETC步枪"

#: .\items\gun\abstract.json
msgid "2 charges ETC rifle"
msgid_plural "2 charges ETC rifles"
msgstr[0] "2发装药ETC步枪"

#: .\items\gun\abstract.json
msgid "EC ammo ETC rifle with manual actions"
msgid_plural "EC ammo ETC rifles with manual actions"
msgstr[0] "EC弹药手动操作ETC步枪"

#: .\items\gun\abstract.json
msgid "ETC rifle with manual actions"
msgid_plural "ETC rifles with manual actions"
msgstr[0] "手动操作ETC步枪"

#: .\items\gun\abstract.json
msgid "2 charges ETC rifle with manual actions"
msgid_plural "2 charges ETC rifle with manual actions"
msgstr[0] "2发装药手动操作ETC步枪"

#: .\items\gun\abstract.json
msgid "base ETC SMG"
msgid_plural "base ETC SMGs"
msgstr[0] "基础ETC冲锋枪"

#: .\items\gun\barrel.json .\items\gunmod\barrel.json
msgid "OFG16k air-filled barrel"
msgid_plural "OFG16k air-filled barrels"
msgstr[0] "OFG16k充气枪管"

#. ~ Use action menu_text for {'str': 'OFG16k air-filled barrel'}.
#: .\items\gun\barrel.json .\items\gunmod\barrel.json
msgid "Prepare hydrogen"
msgstr "准备氢气"

#. ~ Use action msg for {'str': 'OFG16k air-filled barrel'}.
#: .\items\gun\barrel.json .\items\gunmod\barrel.json
msgid ""
"You prepare the canister to fill up the barrel and replace atmospheric air "
"with pure hydrogen."
msgstr "你准备好气罐，将枪管充满并用纯氢替换大气空气。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'OFG16k air-filled barrel'}
#: .\items\gun\barrel.json .\items\gunmod\barrel.json
msgid ""
"The barrel of the OFG16k filled with atmospheric air, resulting in "
"suboptimal muzzle velocity but far more reliable action, plus its gas "
"loading and sealing mechanisms and emergency release. Remove from the "
"OFG16k, load a canister and activate to fill it with hydrogen."
msgstr ""
"OFG16k枪管充满大气空气，导致枪口初速不理想但动作可靠性更高，附带其气体装填与密封机制以及紧急释放装置。从OFG16k上取下，装入气罐并激活以填充氢气。"

#: .\items\gun\barrel.json .\items\gunmod\barrel.json
msgid "OFG16k hydrogen-filled barrel"
msgid_plural "OFG16k hydrogen-filled barrels"
msgstr[0] "OFG16k充氢枪管"

#. ~ Use action menu_text for {'str': 'OFG16k hydrogen-filled barrel'}.
#: .\items\gun\barrel.json .\items\gunmod\barrel.json
msgid "Vent off hydrogen"
msgstr "排放氢气"

#. ~ Use action msg for {'str': 'OFG16k hydrogen-filled barrel'}.
#: .\items\gun\barrel.json .\items\gunmod\barrel.json
msgid ""
"You vent off hydrogen, expose the barrel to atmospheric air and discard the "
"now empty canister."
msgstr "你排放氢气，将枪管暴露于大气中并丢弃已空的气罐。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'OFG16k hydrogen-filled barrel'}
#: .\items\gun\barrel.json .\items\gunmod\barrel.json
msgid ""
"The barrel of the OFG16k filled with pure hydrogen from an attached "
"canister. The speed of sound is 3.8 times faster inside it, which "
"drastically boosts muzzle velocity. Included with it are the gas loading and"
" sealing mechanisms and emergency release. Activate to vent off all hydrogen"
" and unseal it to the atmosphere."
msgstr ""
"OFG16k枪管充满来自连接气罐的纯氢。内部声速快3.8倍，大幅提升枪口初速。附带气体装填与密封机制以及紧急释放装置。激活以排放所有氢气并解除密封至大气。"

#: .\items\gun\barrel.json .\items\gunmod\barrel.json
msgid "OCG ER555 standard barrel"
msgid_plural "OCG ER555 standard barrels"
msgstr[0] "OCG ER555标准枪管"

#: .\items\gun\barrel.json .\items\gunmod\barrel.json
msgid ""
"An OCG standard 5.56mm barrel. Long enough for sniper rifles as it is when "
"used together with electrothermal-chemical technology."
msgstr "OCG标准5.56毫米枪管。长度足以用作狙击步枪枪管，尤其与电热化学技术结合使用时。"

#: .\items\gun\barrel.json .\items\gunmod\barrel.json
msgid "OCG ER555 shortened barrel"
msgid_plural "OCG ER555 shortened barrels"
msgstr[0] "OCG ER555短枪管"

#: .\items\gun\barrel.json .\items\gunmod\barrel.json
msgid ""
"An OCG built in shortened 5.56mm barrel, making a gun easier to carry, "
"maneuver and aim at the expense of damage, accuracy and range. Its handguard"
" rails support two underbarrel attachments."
msgstr "OCG内置短5.56毫米枪管，使枪支更易携带、操控和瞄准，但牺牲伤害、精度和射程。其护木导轨支持两个下挂附件。"

#: .\items\gun\barrel.json .\items\gunmod\barrel.json
msgid "OCG ER555 CQB barrel"
msgid_plural "OCG ER555 CQB barrels"
msgstr[0] "OCG ER555 CQB枪管"

#: .\items\gun\barrel.json .\items\gunmod\barrel.json
msgid ""
"An OCG built in very short 5.56mm barrel for close quarters battle, making a"
" gun much easier to carry, maneuver and aim at the expense of damage, "
"accuracy and range. Its handguard rails support two underbarrel attachments."
msgstr "OCG内置极短5.56毫米枪管，用于近距离战斗，使枪支更易携带、操控和瞄准，但牺牲伤害、精度和射程。其护木导轨支持两个下挂附件。"

#: .\items\gun\barrel.json .\items\gunmod\barrel.json
msgid "OCG ER555 reinforced barrel"
msgid_plural "OCG ER555 reinforced barrels"
msgstr[0] "OCG ER555强化枪管"

#: .\items\gun\barrel.json .\items\gunmod\barrel.json
msgid ""
"An OCG built in reinforced 5.56mm barrel for the E/QR555-SAW. Improves the "
"gun's reliability."
msgstr "OCG内置强化5.56毫米枪管，专为E/QR555-SAW设计。提升枪支可靠性。"

#: .\items\gun\barrel.json .\items\gunmod\barrel.json
msgid "OCG QR555 DMR barrel"
msgid_plural "OCG QR555 DMR barrels"
msgstr[0] "OCG QR555 DMR枪管"

#: .\items\gun\barrel.json .\items\gunmod\barrel.json
msgid ""
"An OCG DMR 5.56mm match-grade barrel, extending the effective range of "
"subsonic 5.56 OCG Blackout rounds beyond 300 meters and of regular 5.56 NATO"
" beyond 400 while maintaining the the former subsonic."
msgstr ""
"OCG DMR 5.56毫米竞赛级枪管，将亚音速5.56 OCG Blackout弹的有效射程延伸至300米以上，常规5.56 "
"NATO弹延伸至400米以上，同时保持前者亚音速特性。"

#: .\items\gun\magpin.json
msgid "OCG GC166 Gauss carbine"
msgid_plural "OCG GC166 Gauss carbines"
msgstr[0] "OCG GC166高斯卡宾枪"

#: .\items\gun\magpin.json
msgid ""
"A milspec bullpup coilgun which can shoot proprietary OmniCorp magpins and, "
"with reduced efficiency, DIY flechettes and nails. Fed by UPS and a "
"120-round helical magazine. Bulky due to its capacitor and thick ceramic "
"reinforced barrel but very compact in length."
msgstr ""
"一款军用规格的无托式线圈枪，可发射专用的OmniCorp磁钉，并能以较低效率发射自制箭弹与钉子。由UPS和120发螺旋弹匣供弹。因电容器和厚重的陶瓷增强枪管而显得笨重，但长度上非常紧凑。"

#: .\items\gun\shot.json
msgid "Modified L12 Defender"
msgid_plural "Modified L12 Defender"
msgstr[0] "改装型L12防御者"

#: .\items\gun\shot.json
msgid ""
"A custom made L12 Defender for one of Leadworks LLC VIP executives, its "
"furniture was replaced with a more lightweight one to make wielding it with "
"only one hand easier at the expense of more recoil. Surprisingly compact "
"thanks to its moving barrel and forward-back pump mechanism. Like most other"
" Leadworks products it doesn't accept third-party modifications."
msgstr ""
"为Leadworks LLC的一位VIP高管定制的L12防御者，其枪身被替换为更轻量化的部件，以便单手操作，但代价是后坐力更大。得益于可动枪管和前-"
"后泵动机制，其紧凑程度令人惊讶。与大多数其他Leadworks产品一样，它不接受第三方改装。"

#: .\items\gun\shot.json
msgid "OCG12 Excidia"
msgid_plural "OCG12 Excidia"
msgstr[0] "OCG12 灭世者"

#: .\items\gun\shot.json
msgid ""
"Perhaps the pinnacle of overkill, OmniCorp Excidia is an automatic double "
"barrel shotgun. Contains two improved chokes, magazines and mirrored "
"ejection ports, but only one trigger: fire modes are set through a selector "
"lever. Its action only supports double shots or full auto. Uses two stacked "
"Saiga-12 or proprietary magazines."
msgstr ""
"或许是过度杀伤的巅峰之作，OmniCorp灭世者是一款自动双管霰弹枪。包含两个改进的收束器、弹匣和镜像抛壳口，但只有一个扳机：射击模式通过选择杆设定。其动作仅支持双发或全自动射击。使用两个堆叠的Saiga-12或专用弹匣。"

#: .\items\gun\shot.json
msgid "OCG12-S Scuta"
msgid_plural "OCG12-S Scuta"
msgstr[0] "OCG12-S 盾卫"

#: .\items\gun\shot.json
msgid ""
"A less overkill, semi automatic version of the Omnicorp Excidia double "
"barrel shotgun minus its built-in accessories and a double trigger instead "
"of a fire selector lever, supporting single shots. Smaller thanks to its "
"telescopic stock, but with greater felt recoil. Uses two stacked Saiga-12 or"
" proprietary magazines."
msgstr ""
"Omnicorp灭世者双管霰弹枪的半自动版本，杀伤力稍减，移除了内置配件，并采用双扳机而非射击模式选择杆，支持单发射击。得益于伸缩枪托，尺寸更小，但感觉后坐力更大。使用两个堆叠的Saiga-12或专用弹匣。"

#: .\items\gunmod\mechanism.json
msgid "N8 high density capacitor"
msgid_plural "N8 high density capacitors"
msgstr[0] "N8高密度电容器"

#: .\items\gunmod\mechanism.json
msgid ""
"A capacitor for the Nanogun's boosted electrothermal-chemical action, which "
"improves armor penetration at the cost of more power consumption, noise and "
"recoil."
msgstr "用于纳米枪增强型电热化学动作的电容器，可提高穿甲能力，但代价是更高的功耗、噪音和后坐力。"

#: .\items\gunmod\mechanism.json
msgid "mechanism"
msgstr "机械装置"

#: .\items\gunmod\mechanism.json
msgid "MS400 high density capacitor"
msgid_plural "MS400 high density capacitors"
msgstr[0] "MS400高密度电容器"

#: .\items\gunmod\mechanism.json
msgid ""
"A capacitor for the overcharged MS400 electrothermal-chemical action, which "
"improves damage, effective range and armor penetration at the cost of more "
"power consumption, noise and recoil."
msgstr "用于过载MS400电热化学动作的电容器，可提高伤害、有效射程和穿甲能力，但代价是更高的功耗、噪音和后坐力。"

#: .\items\gunmod\mechanism.json
msgid "OCG anti-drone capacitor"
msgid_plural "OCG anti-drone capacitors"
msgstr[0] "OCG反无人机电容器"

#: .\items\gunmod\mechanism.json
msgid ""
"A capacitor for overcharged 5.56 ETC caliber electrothermal-chemical guns, "
"improving penetration against the heaviest drone and power armors at the "
"cost of much more power consumption, noise and recoil."
msgstr "用于过载5.56 ETC口径电热化学枪的电容器，可提高对重型无人机和动力装甲的穿透力，但代价是更高的功耗、噪音和后坐力。"

#: .\items\gunmod\muzzle.json
msgid "MR9SD integral suppressor"
msgid_plural "MR9SD integral suppressors"
msgstr[0] "MR9SD一体式消音器"

#: .\items\gunmod\muzzle.json
msgid "The integrated suppressor for the MR9SD Styx."
msgstr "MR9SD冥河的一体式消音器。"

#: .\items\gunmod\muzzle.json
msgid "barrel"
msgstr "枪管"

#: .\items\gunmod\muzzle.json
msgid "MS400SD integral suppressor"
msgid_plural "MS400SD integral suppressors"
msgstr[0] "MS400SD一体式消音器"

#: .\items\gunmod\muzzle.json
msgid "A complex and heavy integrated suppressor for a hypervelocity gun."
msgstr "一款复杂而沉重的一体式消音器，适用于超高速枪械。"

#: .\items\gunmod\muzzle.json
msgid "N8SD integral suppressors"
msgid_plural "N8SD integral suppressorss"
msgstr[0] "N8SD一体式消音器"

#: .\items\gunmod\muzzle.json
msgid "Six integrated suppressors for the N8SD nanogun barrels."
msgstr "用于N8SD纳米枪枪管的六个一体式消音器。"

#: .\items\gunmod\muzzle.json
msgid "O2038HSD integral suppressor"
msgid_plural "O2038HSD integral suppressors"
msgstr[0] "O2038HSD一体式消音器"

#: .\items\gunmod\muzzle.json
msgid "Integrated suppressor for the O2038HSD."
msgstr "O2038HSD的一体式消音器。"

#: .\items\gunmod\muzzle.json
msgid "O2038SD integral suppressor"
msgid_plural "O2038SD integral suppressors"
msgstr[0] "O2038SD一体式消音器"

#: .\items\gunmod\muzzle.json
msgid "Integrated suppressor for the O2038SD."
msgstr "O2038SD的一体式消音器。"

#: .\items\gunmod\muzzle.json
msgid "QR555 integral suppressor"
msgid_plural "QR555 integral suppressors"
msgstr[0] "QR555一体式消音器"

#: .\items\gunmod\muzzle.json
msgid ""
"Integrated suppressor for the \"Quiet\" Rifle 555 platform, it won't make "
"justice to such name without 5.56x45mm or 5.56 OCG Blackout subsonic loads."
msgstr "“寂静”步枪555平台的一体式消音器，若不使用5.56x45mm或5.56 OCG Blackout亚音速弹药，则名不副实。"

#: .\items\gunmod\muzzle.json
msgid "SMP integral suppressor"
msgid_plural "SMP integral suppressors"
msgstr[0] "SMP一体式消音器"

#: .\items\gunmod\muzzle.json
msgid "Integrated suppressor for the Stealth Machine Pistol."
msgstr "隐形冲锋枪的一体式消音器。"

#: .\items\gunmod\muzzle.json
msgid "Stealth Pistol integral suppressor"
msgid_plural "Stealth Pistol integral suppressors"
msgstr[0] "隐形手枪一体式消音器"

#: .\items\gunmod\muzzle.json
msgid ""
"Integrated suppressor for the Stealth Pistol, curiously made of a ceramic "
"matrix composite."
msgstr "隐形手枪的一体式消音器，奇特的是由陶瓷基复合材料制成。"

#: .\items\gunmod\rail.json
msgid "OCG gyroscopic stabilizer"
msgid_plural "OCG gyroscopic stabilizers"
msgstr[0] "OCG陀螺稳定器"

#: .\items\gunmod\rail.json
msgid "An advanced OCG built in gyroscopic stabilizer."
msgstr "一款先进的OCG内置陀螺稳定器。"

#: .\items\gunmod\stock.json
msgid "OCG recoil stock"
msgid_plural "OCG recoil stocks"
msgstr[0] "OCG后坐力枪托"

#: .\items\gunmod\stock.json
msgid "An advanced OCG built in stock designed to absorb perceived recoil."
msgstr "一款先进的OCG内置枪托，旨在吸收感知后坐力。"

#: .\items\gunmod\stock.json
msgid "OCG telescopic stock"
msgid_plural "OCG telescopic stocks"
msgstr[0] "OCG伸缩枪托"

#: .\items\gunmod\stock.json
msgid ""
"An OCG built in telescopic stock which is faster to set up than a folding "
"stock but won't reduce as much volume."
msgstr "一款OCG内置伸缩枪托，比折叠枪托展开更快，但体积缩减效果较差。"

#: .\items\gunmod\underbarrel.json
msgid "grip/pod bipod"
msgid_plural "grip/pod bipods"
msgstr[0] "握把/脚架两用支架"

#: .\items\gunmod\underbarrel.json
msgid ""
"All-in-one bipod and forward grip for recoil control. This is the bipod "
"component, usable only on certain surfaces, a bit less effective than a "
"dedicated bipod but faster to equip."
msgstr "一体式脚架与前握把，用于控制后坐力。此为脚架组件，仅可在特定表面使用，效果略逊于专用脚架但装备更快。"

#: .\items\gunmod\underbarrel.json
msgid "grip/pod forward grip"
msgid_plural "grip/pod forward grips"
msgstr[0] "握把/脚架前握把"

#: .\items\gunmod\underbarrel.json
msgid ""
"All-in-one bipod and forward grip for recoil control. This is the grip "
"component, it is slightly less effective than a dedicated forward grip."
msgstr "一体式脚架与前握把，用于控制后坐力。此为握把组件，效果略逊于专用前握把。"

#: .\items\gunmod\underbarrel.json
msgid "RM42I bayonet"
msgid_plural "RM42I bayonets"
msgstr[0] "RM42I刺刀"

#: .\items\gunmod\underbarrel.json
msgid ""
"A licensed integrated variant of the RM42 fighting knife for the ER555-CQB "
"and QR555-SMG with a shorter blade."
msgstr "RM42战斗刀的授权集成变体，适配ER555-CQB和QR555-SMG，采用更短的刀身。"

#: .\items\gunmod\underbarrel.json
msgid "bayonet"
msgstr "刺刀"

#: .\items\gunmod\underbarrel.json
msgid "underbarrel"
msgstr "下挂式"

#: .\items\magazine\1magmg.json
msgid "GG285 Magazine"
msgid_plural "GG285 Magazines"
msgstr[0] "GG285弹匣"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'GG285 Magazine'}
#: .\items\magazine\1magmg.json
msgid ""
"A 300-round horizontal helical magazine which fits in the frame of the GG285"
" Gauss Gun."
msgstr "300发水平螺旋弹匣，适配GG285高斯枪的框架。"

#: .\items\magazine\223.json
msgid "OCM5-14 STANAG small magazine"
msgid_plural "OCM5-14 STANAG small magazines"
msgstr[0] "OCM5-14 STANAG小型弹匣"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'OCM5-14 STANAG small magazine'}
#: .\items\magazine\223.json
msgid ""
"A compact 14-round 5.56 NATO magazine compatible with STANAG rifles, an "
"alternative to the older Ruger 5.56x45mm mag, it is almost identical to its "
"version for 5.56 Electrothermal."
msgstr "紧凑型14发5.56 NATO弹匣，兼容STANAG步枪，可作为老式鲁格5.56x45mm弹匣的替代品，与5.56电热版本几乎相同。"

#: .\items\magazine\223.json
msgid "OCM5-24 STANAG casket magazine"
msgid_plural "OCM5-24 STANAG casket magazines"
msgstr[0] "OCM5-24 STANAG盒式弹匣"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'OCM5-24 STANAG casket magazine'}
#: .\items\magazine\223.json
msgid ""
"A lightweight 24-round 5.56 NATO casket magazine compatible with STANAG "
"rifles, almost identical to its version for 5.56 Electrothermal. Amazingly "
"compact but less reliable and tricky to reload."
msgstr "轻量化24发5.56 NATO盒式弹匣，兼容STANAG步枪，与5.56电热版本几乎相同。极其紧凑但可靠性较低且装填较麻烦。"

